lines: NONE OF SELF AND ALL OF THEE
Nzizyangu taku cako, Nzizyangu taku cako,
Kaambo kangu Mufutuli acisamu waka yaswa,
Kuli kwangu a kwako, Kuli kwangu a kwako,
Moyo wangu wazumina, ÒKuli kwangu a kwako.Ó
Luse lwakwe lusilika, Lugwasya bantu boonse,
Kunji tola nku kwako, Kunji tola nku kwako,
Kwandipa kuti nzumine, ÒKunji tola nku kwako.Ó
Luyando lwako luteeli, Luinda zintu zyoonse,
Ndazumina lino Mwami, ÒKoonse tola nku kwako,Ó
Koonse tola nku kwako, Koonse tola nku kwako,
Ndazumina lino Mwami, ÒKoonse tola nku kwako.Ó
